discuss-on-wiki-text: $1 e $2 em $3 [[User:$4]] ([[User talk:$4|disc]] | [[Special:Contributions/$4|contribs]]) e [[User:$5]] ([[User talk:$5|disc]] | [[Special:Contributions/$5|contribs]]) editaram ambos algumas páginas em comum.
